    "ChatGPT、Claude、Midjourney 都在你的订阅栏里安家。早上跟 AI 写代码,晚上跟 AI 写日记 —— 智能时代的常住居民,大概就长你这样。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney — alle wohnen in deiner Abo-Liste. Morgens mit KI coden, abends mit KI Tagebuch führen."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney — they all live in your subscription list. Coding with AI in the morning, journaling with AI at night. A native of the AI era looks a lot like you."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney viven en tu lista. Por la mañana programas con IA, por la noche escribes diarios con IA."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney habitent ta liste. Le matin tu codes avec l’IA, le soir tu écris ton journal avec l’IA."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT、Claude、Midjourney — みんなあなたのサブスク欄に住んでいます。朝は AI とコード、夜は AI と日記。AI 時代の住人はきっとあなたのような人。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT, Claude, Midjourney — 모두 당신의 구독 리스트에 살고 있어요. 아침엔 AI 와 코딩, 밤엔 AI 와 일기. AI 시대의 원주민이 바로 당신."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ChatGPT、Claude、Midjourney 都在你的訂閱欄裡安家。早上跟 AI 寫程式,晚上跟 AI 寫日記 —— 智能時代的常住居民,大概就長你這樣。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Duolingo、Coursera、Masterclass、Skillshare —— 你相信每一个订阅都是对未来自己的投资。永不停歇地往前走。": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo, Coursera, Masterclass, Skillshare — jedes Abo ist eine Investition in dein zukünftiges Ich."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo, Coursera, Masterclass, Skillshare — every subscription is an investment in tomorrow's you."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo, Coursera, Masterclass, Skillshare — cada suscripción es una inversión en tu yo futuro."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo, Coursera, Masterclass, Skillshare — chaque abo est un investissement dans le toi de demain."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo、Coursera、Masterclass、Skillshare。すべての登録は未来の自分への投資。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo, Coursera, Masterclass, Skillshare — 모든 구독은 미래의 자신에 대한 투자."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Duolingo、Coursera、Masterclass、Skillshare —— 你相信每一個訂閱都是對未來自己的投資。永不停歇地往前走。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
