    "Notion、Things、Obsidian、Raycast,你的工具像精密的齿轮咬合在一起。每个 task 都有它的位置,每个想法都不会丢。": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Notion, Things, Obsidian, Raycast — deine Tools greifen wie Zahnräder ineinander."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Notion, Things, Obsidian, Raycast — your tools mesh like precision gears. Every task has its spot, every idea finds a home."
          }
