    "记账 App、理财软件、投资平台,你认真对待每一分钱。你的人生有 budget、有 forecast、有月度 review。": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haushalts-Apps, Finanz-Tracker, Anlage-Plattformen — du nimmst jeden Cent ernst."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Budget apps, finance trackers, investment platforms — you run your life on budgets, forecasts, and monthly reviews."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apps de presupuesto, gestores financieros, plataformas de inversión — te tomas cada euro en serio."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apps de budget, outils financiers, plateformes d’investissement — tu prends chaque euro au sérieux."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "家計簿、資産管理、投資プラットフォーム。一円も真剣に。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "가계부, 자산 관리, 투자 플랫폼 — 모든 돈을 진지하게."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "記帳 App、理財軟體、投資平台,你認真對待每一分錢。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
